        "narrative": "Completion of all Student Learning Targets (SLTs) for this course module:\n  1. I can find a bug in the Cardano XP app.\n  2. I can request a feature for Cardano XP.\n  3. I can share an idea for how to use Cardano XP.\n\nOn-chain anchor: Cardano native token under policy 76bab08586cbd53003bfec0e63bc3165fd73afb99cbfa9f4e8157742 (preprod). The credential NFT is minted to the recipient's wallet by the Andamio v2 protocol's credential_claim transaction."
